The paper deals with natural language question answering and incorporates external knowledge sources to improve performance. This suggests that it could fall under the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of information retrieval (IR) also suggests a potential fit for information retrieval (cs.IR) and the exploration of different strategies for using knowledge could fall under computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CC).
